body:
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

I don&#039;t understand how Riot works.  They love the excuse that they have separate departments for doing everything which of course gives all these departments plausible deniability when shit hits the fan, which it does frequently, but why is this guy balancing his own mess.  You&#039;re asking this one guy, who couldn&#039;t tell Camille was going to be a fucking stupid as fuck champion to begin with, to try and objectively analyze where his design went wrong, essentially asking him to call himself out.  

Omg is this why Riot keeps beating around the bush for so many problematic champions, you give their balancing back to the people who made them who are naturally vested in trying to not look like stupid failures.   Why.  Whyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy.
